data.description: Breathtaking views! Perfect spot for entertaining or relaxing. Witness glorious sunrises and spectacular views of the mountains, valley, and golf course. In the afternoon/evening the sunsets are picturesque from the front, and are just as amazing from the shaded back patio, as the sun reflects off the mountains in the distance. Easy access to dining, shopping, wineries, parks, golf, and the freeway, you are in the prime location for peace and serenity, without giving up any conveniences. This home is perfectly situated on 1.59 acres of beautiful, mature landscaping, avocado trees, and a few citrus trees. Enjoy the newer circular drive which provides ample parking and the home has a perfect spot for the RV with views and full hookups. The outside has recently received a major renovation with a dog run, rear landscaping, a continuation of an additional patio space with pavers and a built-in BBQ. When you step inside, you are met with stunning new flooring, a large open space for entertaining, wood beamed ceilings, an open concept kitchen with large island, a newer stove, brand new dishwasher, and double ovens. The primary suite was just updated with freestanding tub, separate tile shower, dual sinks, and a large walk-in closet. On the other side of the house, you will find a junior suite with newly remodeled ensuite bath. The recently remodeled laundry room has ample storage, sink, and convenient shelf just above the appliances. This home is a must see!! Virtual tour link has a video of the property.
